            <title>[CAMEL-2972] onException not working correctly when using routeContext</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-2972</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using a routeContext, the last (in the xml-file) defined route-scoped &amp;lt;onException&amp;gt; configuration is shared by the other routes in the context.&lt;/p&gt;

